{"title":"花将开得比任何时代更鲜美","authors":["姜秀珍"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":11,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"花将开得比任何时代更鲜美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安徽民间歌手  姜秀珍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回想几年前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是“牛鬼”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关在牛棚里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天三请罪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文坛恶霸放飞刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各级文联砍粉碎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电影戏剧被枪毙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族文化全灭毁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看在眼，痛在心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一腔热血遭冰水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天昏地暗乌云盖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毒得空气都发霉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天感谢党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们成宝贝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"派到首都来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参加文代会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家走到机舱里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心情激动掉热泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们这些老金牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插上翅膀尽情飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人在飞啊心在飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大祖国也在飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向四个现代化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把失去的时间快追回。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代表到旅社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老友喜相会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时隔十九年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也难认谁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年刀山滚过来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失去多少老前辈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家见面第一句："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都是幸存者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑发折磨变白发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好人被摧成残废，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天虽然人归队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艺术青春却难归。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艺苑开盛会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党又送春回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听到好报告，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻几十岁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说头上尽白发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们还是红小鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党又给戴上红领巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们参加少先队。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重整旗鼓再出征，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焕发青春劲百倍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为四化谱写新战歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献出一切力量和智慧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民关心的文艺花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在民主树上绽蓓蕾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等到来年春三月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花将开得比任何时代更鲜美！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}